  - m_Id: 521961672704
    m_Localized: "\xA1\xA1\xA1\xA1OMG!!!!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 31865638912
    m_Localized: "\xA1\xA1\xA1\xA1OMG!!!!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 70235131904
    m_Localized: '!Pepe! I''m here!!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 95027662848
    m_Localized: Hmm... I don't think so...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 210308108288
    m_Localized: What do you mean? It said right at the top that you were here...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 257976373248
    m_Localized: I'm afraid this is only the beginning...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 326024761344
    m_Localized: You still have the mangroves to see...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 370543104000
    m_Localized: ...the dark and gloomy caves....
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 408820322304
    m_Localized: ...the fierce storm...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 449177915392
    m_Localized: ...before reaching heaven...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
